p: Witness the Honorable Frank Allyn Judge of the said District Court and the Seal of said Court this day of 19th A.D. 1887

I hereby certify that I received the within Warrant on the 20th day of September AD 1887 and served the same onthe 20th day of September AD 1887 by arresting and takinginto custody the following within named defendants Gus Beudjus, Robert Strougland, whose true name is Robert Straugland, Ben Fredrickson, Frank Nelson, Andrew Johnson, Leander Brown, John Thompson, Alex Agreu and Thomas Jacobs and court not then being in session. I did on the 19th day of October AD 1887 accept bail from the following named persons to wit Gus Beudjus, Robert Stranglaud, Ben Fredrickson, Frank Nelson, Andrew Johnson, Leander Brown, Alex Agreu and Thomas Jacobs Budelioned.That they appear at the next regular term of the District Court to be held for Chehalis County, and from term to term thereafter or until duly cleared by due process of law. On accepter of said bail I discharged said parties from custody, and I have been unable after dusuud delivered search to find any of the others of the defendants named in the within warrent
Dated this 14th day of November AD 1887
